query:
INSERT INTO webhook_event_types (code, name, description, category) VALUES
('connector_failure', 'Connector Failure', 'Triggered when a data connector fails to fetch data', 'alerts'),
('connector_recovery', 'Connector Recovery', 'Triggered when a failed connector recovers', 'alerts'),
('stale_data_warning', 'Stale Data Warning', 'Triggered when data exceeds warning threshold', 'alerts'),
('stale_data_critical', 'Stale Data Critical', 'Triggered when data exceeds critical threshold', 'alerts'),
('new_data_available', 'New Data Available', 'Triggered when new data is ingested', 'data'),
('data_anomaly_detected', 'Data Anomaly Detected', 'Triggered when unusual data patterns are detected', 'data'),
('exchange_rate_spike', 'Exchange Rate Spike', 'Triggered when exchange rate changes significantly', 'data'),
('new_publication', 'New Publication', 'Triggered when a new research publication is added', 'publications'),
('publication_updated', 'Publication Updated', 'Triggered when a publication is updated', 'publications'),
('system_health_warning', 'System Health Warning', 'Triggered when system health degrades', 'system'),
('scheduler_job_failed', 'Scheduler Job Failed', 'Triggered when a scheduled job fails', 'system'),
('user_signup', 'New User Signup', 'Triggered when a new user registers', 'system')
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE name=VALUES(name);
